				<p class="hero-sub">
					{'The successor to '}
					<a
						href="https://github.com/infernojs/inferno"
						target="_blank"
						rel="noreferrer"
					>{'Inferno'}</a>
					{', carrying its performance-first goal forward: the hooks, Suspense and ' +
						'actions API you already know, compiled ahead of time. No virtual DOM. ' +
						'No rules of hooks.'}
				</p>
				<div class="hero-actions">
